    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072370_24_4034-4082",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "4034-4082",
      "markText": "美国的家长倾向于将背离某种模式看作是创造力的表现，而努瓦阿图的家长倾向于将精确模仿能力等同于才能",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072370&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=4034&rangeEnd=4082",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ed32170813ab82c5g010588?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=4034&rangeEnd=4082"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072370_28_1378-1427",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "1378-1427",
      "markText": "这种神经修剪以一种特定的方式发生：在此期间不断使用的神经突触被保留下来，而未使用的神经突触将被消除",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072370&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=1378&rangeEnd=1427",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ed32170813ab82c5g010588?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=1378&rangeEnd=1427"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072370_21_3770-3824",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "3770-3824",
      "markText": "·如果学生把自己看作学习者和思考者（亦即利用元认知途径进行学习和教学），那么他们的学习会最成功且会自我维继。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072370&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=3770&rangeEnd=3824",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ed32170813ab82c5g010588?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=3770&rangeEnd=3824"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072370_28_7430-7518",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "7430-7518",
      "markText": "学习轨迹通常受所寓居社群的期望和训练实践的巨大影响。个体并不能无限地去适应，但是当给予机会和支持时，他们能够成长而达到文化所期望的程度，这是让人感叹的(impressive)。",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072370&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=7430&rangeEnd=7518",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ed32170813ab82c5g010588?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=7430&rangeEnd=7518"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072370_24_5011-5050",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "5011-5050",
      "markText": "在帮助学生理解和组织世界的基本认知发展过程（如记忆和感知）中，文化发挥了作用。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072370&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=5011&rangeEnd=5050",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ed32170813ab82c5g010588?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=5011&rangeEnd=5050"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072370_37_1155-1252",
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "range": "1155-1252",
      "markText": "学习策略的有效性受到学习者现有技能和先前知识、学习材料的性质及学习目标等境脉性因素的影响。因此，为了有效地应用这些策略，需要仔细考虑它们的特定机制如何对特定的学习者、场境和学习目标起到有利作用。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072370&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=1155&rangeEnd=1252",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ed32170813ab82c5g010588?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=1155&rangeEnd=1252"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072370_31_1200-1292",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "1200-1292",
      "markText": "存储隐喻没有搞清楚的一个事实是：学习实际上涉及的是基于过去的经验和当前环境中的线索来重建记忆的技能，而不是单纯地对经验副本进行再现。",
      "totalCount": 52,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072370&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=1200&rangeEnd=1292",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ed32170813ab82c5g010588?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=1200&rangeEnd=1292"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072370_14_1678-1706",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "1678-1706",
      "markText": "记忆涉及重建，而不单纯是提取经过编码的心智表征的精确副本",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072370&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1678&rangeEnd=1706",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ed32170813ab82c5g010588?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1678&rangeEnd=1706"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072370_27_16435-16503",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "16435-16503",
      "markText": "事实学习不必是死记硬背的：当学习者精心地将新信息与其已有的其他知识相联系，学习效果就会得到提高（Craik和Tulving,1975）。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072370&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=16435&rangeEnd=16503",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ed32170813ab82c5g010588?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=16435&rangeEnd=16503"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072370_33_1662-1709",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "1662-1709",
      "markText": "任何一个学习事件的信息在随后被提取时，新旧记忆痕迹中的元素都会被重新激活，并同时可用于重新整合",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072370&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=1662&rangeEnd=1709",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ed32170813ab82c5g010588?chapterUid=33&rangeStart=1662&rangeEnd=1709"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072370_14_772-832",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "772-832",
      "markText": "学习在人的一生中改变着脑，同时，脑又在人的整个生命时期以影响学习的方式发展着，而这些方式又受到学习者的境脉和文化的影响。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072370&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=772&rangeEnd=832",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ed32170813ab82c5g010588?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=772&rangeEnd=832"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072370_25_2474-2514",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "2474-2514",
      "markText": "情绪是思维中一个基本且无处不在的维度，情绪的处理过程引导着行为、思考和学习的方向",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072370&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=2474&rangeEnd=2514",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ed32170813ab82c5g010588?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=2474&rangeEnd=2514"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072370_34_1525-1564",
      "chapterUid": 34,
      "range": "1525-1564",
      "markText": "学习的一个主要目标是知道到哪里寻找资源和帮助，这一能力在信息时代仍然十分重要。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072370&chapterUid=34&rangeStart=1525&rangeEnd=1564",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ed32170813ab82c5g010588?chapterUid=34&rangeStart=1525&rangeEnd=1564"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072370_15_608-666",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "608-666",
      "markText": "先前知识也可能带来偏向，导致人们注意不到新的信息并依赖现有模式来解决新问题。这些偏向只有通过有意识的努力才能被克服。",
      "totalCount": 44,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072370&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=608&rangeEnd=666",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ed32170813ab82c5g010588?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=608&rangeEnd=666"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072370_27_10540-10619",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "10540-10619",
      "markText": "没有反馈的学习模式通常需要基于对环境长时间的体验且渐进地发生。以这种方式学习到的规律可能不容易用言语表达，因为它们并不是经由明确的假设检验或测试而得到的结果。",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072370&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=10540&rangeEnd=10619",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ed32170813ab82c5g010588?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=10540&rangeEnd=10619"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072370_24_3876-3959",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "3876-3959",
      "markText": "社会化实践——监护人与儿童交流的方式——决定了儿童如何学习、他们学习什么、他们学得有多快，甚至是学习（包括从走路到如何与人进行社会性互动的所有一切）的发展终点在哪里。",
      "totalCount": 40,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072370&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=3876&rangeEnd=3959",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ed32170813ab82c5g010588?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=3876&rangeEnd=3959"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072370_16_611-677",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "611-677",
      "markText": "如果学校或学习环境能让学习者感受到“归属感”，并且当环境可以提升学习者的能动性和目标感时，各个年龄段的学习者的学习动机都能得到促进。",
      "totalCount": 39,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072370&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=611&rangeEnd=677",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ed32170813ab82c5g010588?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=611&rangeEnd=677"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072370_27_6085-6122",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "6085-6122",
      "markText": "由习惯驱动的行为是普遍存在的，这表明人们的许多行为都没有经过有意识的筛选。",
      "totalCount": 39,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072370&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=6085&rangeEnd=6122",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ed32170813ab82c5g010588?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=6085&rangeEnd=6122"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300072370_15_721-815",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "721-815",
      "markText": "结论5-2　学习者通常会对他们正在积累的信息生成自己的新理解，并通过在信息片段之间建立逻辑联系来有效地扩展他们的知识。这种产生新理解的能力让学习者得以使用他们的知识来概括、分类和解决问题。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300072370&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=721&rangeEnd=815",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ed32170813ab82c5g010588?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=721&rangeEnd=815"
    }
